<Defs>

	<WeatherDef>
		<defName>Thunderstorm</defName>
		<label>Electrical thunderstorm</label>
		<description>Dry thunderstorm generated by strange effect. It seems are very dangerous because the lightning can start fires and there is no rain to put them out.</description>
